---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof for Personal Stylists — Testimonials That Book New Clients | SocialProof"
  description="Collect and display authentic client testimonials for your personal styling business. Let transformation stories sell new clients for you. Free to start."
>
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">For Personal Stylists</p>
        <h1>You change how clients feel about themselves — let that story sell for you</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Personal styling isn't about clothes. It's about confidence, clarity, and finally looking like the person you want to be. SocialProof captures those transformation stories as testimonials that book new clients on autopilot.</p>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="btn btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why personal stylists struggle with social proof</h2>
        <div class="pain-grid">
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>😤 Happy clients forget to post</h3>
            <p>Your client walks out feeling amazing. She tells three friends in person. She never posts a review online. You got none of the credit you deserved publicly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>📸 Instagram only shows the outfits</h3>
            <p>Before/after photos are powerful, but the real story is "I finally feel confident at work" or "I stopped dreading getting dressed." That story isn't in a flat-lay photo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pain-card">
            <h3>🔗 High-ticket services need high-trust proof</h3>
            <p>A $300+ styling session is a big decision. Prospective clients need to see real results from real people before they'll invest. Logos and rates alone don't cut it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SocialProof fixes this in 3 steps</h2>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            <strong>Send a collect link</strong>
            <p>After a session or wardrobe edit, text your client a link. Ask them to describe how they feel now vs. before. That emotional response is your best sales copy.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Approve with one click</strong>
            <p>Review submissions in your dashboard. Approve the testimonials that tell the real story — confidence gained, decision fatigue gone, getting compliments at work.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Embed on your site</strong>
            <p>One script tag on your services page or homepage. Works on Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, or any site builder you use.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Built for Personal Stylists</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>⭐ Star ratings + text</h3>
            <p>Collect written testimonials that tell the transformation story — not just a star rating, but the before and after in the client's own words.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📷 Client photos</h3>
            <p>Let clients attach a photo. A smiling client in their new look is worth a thousand words — and it's way more credible than stock photography.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🎨 Polished, on-brand widget</h3>
            <p>Customize colors and layout to match your aesthetic. The widget looks as curated as your styling boards.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>📱 Easy mobile form</h3>
            <p>Clients fill it on their phone while the excitement is fresh — right after the session or when they wear their new outfits for the first time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🔒 You own the data</h3>
            <p>Testimonials live in your account. Not on Yelp. Not on a platform that can change its algorithm and bury your reviews.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>🆓 Free forever tier</h3>
            <p>1 active widget, unlimited collections. Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card to start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pricing-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. Pro is $9/mo for unlimited everything.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
